1922723 cthe appointment, powers and duties of the officers of the University and their emoluments;
235165 dthe appointment of teachers of the University and other academic staff and their emoluments;
1046234 ethe appointment of teachers and other academic staff working in any other University or organisation for a specified period for undertaking a joint project;
515474 fthe conditions of service of employees including provision for pension, insurance and provident fund, the manner of termination of service and disciplinary action;
683684 gthe principles governing seniority of service of employees;
1846540 hthe procedure for arbitration in cases of dispute between employees or students and the University;
646056 ithe procedure for appeal to the Executive Council by any employee or student against the action of any officer or authority of the University;
