1872907 aexercise general supervision over the funds of the University and shall advise it as regards its financial policy; and
1105163 bperform such other financial functions as may be assigned to him by the Executive Council or as may be prescribed by these Statutes or the Ordinances: Provided that the Finance Officer shall not incur any expenditure or make any investment exceeding ten thousand rupees without the previous approval of the Executive Council.
