1573937 21 Special mode of appointment.
15213 1Notwithstanding anything contained in Statute 20, the Executive Council may invite a person of high academic distinction and professional attainments to accept a post of Professor or Reader or any other academic past in the University, as the case may be on such terms and conditions as it deems fit, and on the person agreeing to do so, appoint him to the post.
